    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/4ea4b4e95cf1e33772b7dd43b4e83c59.poster.avif?t=1771601604\" width=744 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/4ea4b4e95cf1e33772b7dd43b4e83c59.webm?t=1771601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/4ea4b4e95cf1e33772b7dd43b4e83c59.mp4?t=1771601604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款回合制角色扮演游戏概念新颖，巧妙融合了抓耳的歌曲和惊险的战斗。与流行歌手凯登丝一同踏上旅途，圆一场明星梦。<br><br>凯登丝在“知名歌曲大赛”失利之后，明白仅凭自己的单人表演无法打动评委，于是便踏上旅途，往返音符大陆各地，足迹遍布摇滚之都杜兰帝斯、电子舞曲之城露米纳等地，一路结识并招募各地的优秀乐人。然而，远方暗潮涌动……“谐波汇聚”现象正在扰乱世间的音乐能量。黑暗势力暗中谋划，企图破坏音符大陆的自然和声。虽然演出安排并没有拯救世界这一项，但凯登丝和她的伙伴此刻必须挺身而出，守护音乐的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/f3637b199766c20f26f448ebd73ffffd.poster.avif?t=1771601604\" width=898 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/f3637b199766c20f26f448ebd73ffffd.webm?t=1771601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/f3637b199766c20f26f448ebd73ffffd.mp4?t=1771601604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《歌手成名录》可以让你体验前所未有的回合制战斗。战场就是舞台，战况千变万化，你要踩准节拍即时进攻，看准时机融合曲风，打出强力的混搭攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/0f90d25b727d3d7fb7da54e194f0ea8c.poster.avif?t=1771601604\" width=742 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626170/extras/0f90d25b727d3d7fb7da54e194f0ea8c.webm?t=1771601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏完整的电影级音乐演出，涵盖各种音乐风格，均由我们的主要角色奉上。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制动作战斗互动感十足，仿佛亲身参与畅快的演奏表演。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于节奏的战斗玩法：跟着节拍发动攻击，可以造成更高伤害。战况变幻莫测：战斗音乐会实时变化，需要你灵活调整战术，及时适应曲风。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐混搭攻击：组合队友的独特曲风，发动混搭合击，引爆全场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索广袤的音符大陆。这里每一种环境和文化都代表了一种音乐风格。深入地下城，与音乐怪咖和巧妙谜题斗智斗勇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心畅玩：不喜欢场景解谜？一键关闭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对回合战斗没兴趣？别担心，我们懂你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《歌手成名录》中，游戏想怎么玩就怎么玩。</p></li></ul>",
